Texts.Eng: A Taco named Steve
A wonderful grotto. This water looks to be quite refreshing. A swim might be ^green;just what you need^reset;, but look out for ^red;predators beneath the surface^reset;.

Texts.Chs: 随着太阳的升起，行星的气体正逐渐升温，你发现强烈的自然之力似乎减弱了不少。
Texts.Eng: As the sun rises, warming the nascent gas of this world you find that the natural forces seem to calm and rapidly reduce in potence.

Texts.Chs: 小子，你真是个白痴！难道你没感觉到你快死了吗？你现在只需要把等会儿看到的人杀了并吃下他你就可以活命了。
Texts.Eng: Brain, you are an idiot. You are about to die, and all you need to do to stop that problem is ^red;murder and devour^reset; the next person you see. Get on it. Or I'll make you.
Death is an illusion.
Don't forget to jump to your death! How else are you going to make ^green;splatter-cakes^reset;?

Texts.Chs: 你好，由于你受到爆炸性减压或者极端压强的作用，你似乎正在接近死亡的边缘。你应该快速地寻找一处安全区域或者无抵抗的面对^red;死亡^reset;！
Texts.Eng: Greetings! You appear to be rapidly dying due to explosive decompression or extreme pressure. You should seek safetly, and relatively quickly or face ^red;certain death^reset;!

Texts.Chs: 你疯了吗？这里的压强在累积到某种程度之后足以在瞬间杀死你，我建议你要么回去准备一些^orange;抵抗压强^reset;的东西再来探险，要么体验死亡！
Texts.Eng: Have you gone mad? The pressure here is enough to crush you almost instantly! What would possess you to come unprotected? Get some ^orange;pressure protection^reset; or face death!
Hmm. This door appears well sealed. Perhaps some ^orange;Explosive Force^reset; might open it. A grenade, bomb or rocket should do the trick.
I am invincible. I should ^red;prove it by getting shot^reset; in the torso!
I am slowly going crazy. 1-2-3-4-5-6-^red;Meat^reset;. Crazy going slowly am I 6-5-4-3-2-1-^red;Kill^reset;!

Texts.Chs: 我不明白你为什么毫无准备就来到此地，或许你是个白痴？快点离开！你需要可以^orange;抵抗压强^reset;的装备或是道具才能生存下去。
Texts.Eng: I am uncertain why you came here. Are you stupid? This isn't at all a place you are evolved to survive. Get out of there! You need ^orange;pressure protection^reset;!

I appear to be weightless! I should ^orange;immediately remove my armor or air supply^reset; so that I can truly appreciate weightlessness! I'll float better! Plus, I'll be even ^green;more^reset; desirable to the opposite sex!
I bet that swimming in ^orange;molten iron^reset; is both revitalizing and enjoyable.
I can hear ^orange;subtle hints of gutteral sound^reset; over your frequency. Keep an eye out for predators.

Texts.Chs: 我虽然没法帮你，但我还是要提醒你：^red;你仍然处于饥饿状态，你那饕餮食欲正在垂涎于那美味多汁的内脏呢^reset;。你还在等什么？去找点^red;活着的东西^reset;，吃下去吧。
Texts.Eng: I can't help but notice: You're still hungry, and your ^red;hellish maw is not dripping with the viscera of the slain^reset;. What is wrong with you? Eat ^red;sentient species^reset;!
I cannot wait to bleed to death! Yaaaaay!
I forgot that ^orange;breathing liquid^reset; is a great way to help keep in shape! I should probably ^red;remove this stupid air supply^reset; in order to breathe a ton of it!
I hear legends of a ^green;magical cleaning fluid^reset; known as bleach and how ^orange;delicious it is^reset;. Let's find some and ingest!

Texts.Chs: 我应该还有一点肉剩了下来。
Texts.Eng: I should have some meat.

Texts.Chs: 生肉，我想吃生肉。
Texts.Eng: I want to eat raw flesh.
I'm bleeding very badly. I should ^red;definitely consider^reset; bleeding even more! I should ^orange;find something sharp^reset; and see if it fits in my eye socket!
It is common knowledge that ingesting molten metal helps you strengthen your bone structure. Don't miss out on that!
It would appear, based on lifesigns, that you have stumbled onto some sort of nest. Be aware: ^red;one large mutant^reset; has been detected. The ^orange;energy source^reset; we seek is also nearby.

Leaping is fun! I should leap immediately from the nearest cliff! I am certain ^orange;Fun Times^reset; will ensue! Alternatively, try impacting the ground at a high speed! You'll get ^green;free cupcakes^reset;!

Moving fast is amazing! ^orange;Especially downwards at the ground^reset; where the magical sparkles await! You should go ^red;really fast^reset; and ram into the ground to collect ^orange;extra^reset; sparkles!

Texts.Chs: 自然之力彻底改变了这里的气候，随着黑夜的到来，你将会发现环境越来越恶劣。或许你可以等到白天再开始探索。
Texts.Eng: Natural forces change the tide of gasses regularly with day and night cycle. As night approaches, you'll find things get a bit worse on your survival. Perhaps return later.
Neat, it just got a ^green;tiny bit windy outside^reset;. Do you know what that means? Yes! ^orange;That's right!^reset;, it's ^red;MURDER TIME!^reset; Let's find ourselves something to kill!
Ohmygoshohmygoshohmygosh ^orange;OH MY GOSH^reset;! Undiscovered ruins of the ^green;Ancients^reset;! Go! EXPLORE!

Texts.Chs: 对，你现在饿极了。^red;为什么你不吃下你最亲密的朋友呢^reset;？他们可都是养分啊！
Texts.Eng: Okay. You're really getting hungry now. Why haven't you ^red;eaten a close personal friend^reset; yet? They are full of nutrients!
Pinky the Nose Squirrel
Pocket Lint
Remember how much you hate all of existence. Now celebrate that hate by taking a leap of faith off the nearest high ledge and hope for the best!

Texts.Chs: 这恶劣的飓风使得温度正在急剧下降。如果你不想死的话，就快点离开这里。
Texts.Eng: The extreme winds have made the temperature plummet dramatically. You should get out of the wind unless you wish to freeze to death rapidly.
The sharper it is, ^red;the more fun it is to eat^reset;! That's what the old tales say! And they're right!

Texts.Chs: 风中似乎传来了一些声音，在你仔细听完之后，发觉这实在太荒诞了！它告诉你在全身赤裸的情况下，深入硫酸海，在海底你可以发现某些事情！
Texts.Eng: The voices in the wind have informed you of a fantastic sale! It can only be found at the bottom of a Sulphuric Ocean, and only if you're naked! Totally legit! Check it out!
This place is long abandoned, it would seem. At one point this world had a promising outlook. I wonder what happened?
To counter the iron loss from cannibalism-induced bleeding, you must consume liquid iron in copious amounts. it's the easiest way to replenish your iron stores. ^red;Trust me^reset;.
Unless you are exeptionally nimble, you are going to need ^orange;climbing ropes^reset; to get up there. I can detect something beyond, so you might consider investigating when you find some!
Use ^green;all of your energy^reset;, and then ^red;run naked, screaming, into packs of monsters^reset;. There is no other way to make perogies.

Texts.Chs:
^red;警告！这颗星球上的辐射极其危险！^reset;
如果没有适当的防护措施，我不建议你继续探索！
Texts.Eng:
WARNING! RADIATION LEVELS ON THIS PLANET ARE EXTREMELY HAZARDOUS!
You should not attempt further exploration without proper protective equipment!

Texts.Chs:
^red;警告！这颗星球上温度极高！^reset;
如果没有适当的防护措施，我不建议你继续探索！
Texts.Eng:
WARNING! TEMPERATURE ON THIS PLANET IS DANGEROUSLY HIGH!
You should not attempt further exploration without proper protective equipment!

Texts.Chs:
^red;警告！这颗星球上温度极低！^reset;
如果没有适当的防护措施，我不建议你继续探索！
Texts.Eng:
WARNING! TEMPERATURE ON THIS PLANET IS DANGEROUSLY LOW!
You should not attempt further exploration without proper protective equipment!
Wake up, Michael.
We should very quickly recite a ^orange;rousing poem about the pointlessness of existentialism^reset; whilst conducting a ^green;grain-fed orchestra of meat^reset;!

Texts.Chs: 今天可不是平静的一天，极端的风将会大幅度降低你的生存能力，希望你已经做好了防御措施。
Texts.Eng: While it is never exactly a pleasant calm day on a Gas Giant, extreme winds severely increase the effects of the environment. Take extra precautions.

Texts.Chs: 为什么我越来越想吃肉呢？
Texts.Eng: Why do I increasingly feel like I require meat?
Wow. Functioning tech, too! You ^orange;NEED^orange; to check that out! PLEASE! For science!?!?!

Y'know what I ^red;really hate^reset;? Skin! Removing it is clearly the ^orange;most direct way^reset; to gain access to the ^green;magical realm of skinless gnomes^reset;! Do it! ^red;Remove your epidermis!^reset;
You
You are without a doubt the stupidest explorer. Ever. You just teleported onto a ^red;gas giant^reset; without protecting yourself from pressure. Idiot. Enjoy your ^red;imminent death^reset;!
You should start ^red;sleeping in the cargo holds of strangers^reset;, and leaving strange notes in their air ducts. If the mood arises, you could maybe even ^green;steal their face-skin^reset;!

Texts.Chs: 你变得如此愤怒的原因正是因为你饿了！你觉得你的朋友怎么样？他那有弹性的皮肤，撕开来或许可以看到鲜嫩的内脏，相信我，这很容易做到，他并没有防备你，快去把他杀了吧，然后你就可以填饱你的肚子了！
Texts.Eng: You're getting pretty hangry. That means angry and hungry. Because hunger. Food. Have you considered ^red;cannibalism^reset;? It's fast and easy! Try it ! Murder a neighbor! Trust the voices.
Your Mind
Your Toenail

Texts.Chs: ^red;警告：恐惧状态！^reset;这个星球上的某些东西正在使你的大脑变得混乱起来，你甚至没有办法集中自己的注意力，你感觉到自己快要疯了...
Texts.Eng: ^red;ALERT: MENTAL STATE DETERIORATING!^reset; Something is causing your thoughts and feelings to become jumbled. Focus is difficult and you feel yourself going insane...

Texts.Chs: ^red;警告：恐惧状态！^reset;这个星球上的某些东西正在使你的大脑变得混乱起来，你甚至没有办法集中自己的注意力，你感觉到自己快要疯了...
Texts.Eng: ^red;ALERT: MENTAL STATE DETERIORATING!^reset; Your surroundings are causing your thoughts and feelings to become jumbled. Focus is difficult and you feel yourself going insane...

Texts.Chs: ^red;警告：毒性空气！^reset;这里的空气似乎有些黏稠，你发觉你的五感越来越迟钝，身体越来越虚弱。
Texts.Eng: ^red;WARNING: TOXIC ATMOSPHERE!^reset; The air here is thick with some sort of viscosity. It makes you feel sluggish, and you feel yourself getting weaker.
hey, you should try experimenting with radioactive materials by ingesting them! you shouldn't miss on getting all the superpowers!
